instagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=ZhimDisgNHn0cuYYHZbNgw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxMEMZkA2CK8uIk27JZb-99o9LT0arP6e9pJLlAkB1UNg&amp;oe=69CA3D64" alt="Slide 3 fra @petopaj" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (3 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@petopaj</strong></p><p>Three ceramic reliefs. I used the ceramic reliefs to try to find a way of combining smaller stories into one work. Have them talk to each other in all directions. It&#x27;s now slowly working its way into my paintings which was everything I hoped for. More on this later. But for now I will enjoy the process <br/>
